Strings.$ExtensionDesc:
Add EEWCN Custom.JS Data Source to CysTerra.
The differences than the custom.js in original EEWCN includes:
1. *_onfail(), is_*_data() are not used;
2. sound.play() doesn’t support network URL;
3. TTS may not be supported;
4. WebSocket “ping” message is sent via text rather than ping opcode, you may need to handle additional “pong” message in *_onsuccess().
